    "rich_text_E9j9Vg": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "title_ME6itT": {
          "type": "title",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Shop Bulk Wholesale Apparel With No Minimums",
            "title_size": "heading-size--small",
            "seo_h_tag": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_tBmN9r": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Whether you’re printing for customers, building your brand, or stocking up for an upcoming event, our blank apparel selection makes it easy to order exactly what you need. Choose from everyday basics and premium fits, available in bulk or small quantities, all at wholesale pricing.</p><p>Shop wholesale blanks across top categories like <a href=\"/collections/t-shirts\" title=\"Blank T-Shirts\">t-shirts</a>, <a href=\"/collections/hoodies\" title=\"Blank Hoodies\">hoodies</a>, <a href=\"/collections/sweatshirts\" title=\"Blank Sweatshirts\">sweatshirts</a>, <a href=\"/collections/polos\" title=\"Blank Polos\">polos</a>, <a href=\"/collections/hats\" title=\"Blank Hats\">hats</a>, <a href=\"/collections/bags\" title=\"Blank Bags\">bags</a>, and more. With popular brands, consistent quality, and fast delivery, you can keep production moving and stay ready for every order.</p><h4><strong>Why Customers Choose Ninja Blanks For Blank Apparel</strong></h4><ul><li><strong>Free Shipping on $50+:</strong> Qualifying blank orders ship free the same day via UPS Ground. Read our <a href=\"https://ninjatransfers.com/pages/shipping-policy\">Shipping Policy</a> for more information.<br/></li><li><strong>Easy Customization:</strong> Add <a href=\"https://ninjatransfers.com/\" title=\"https://ninjatransfers.com/\">Ninja Transfers DTF Transfers</a> to your blanks for a simple ordering experience.<br/></li><li><strong>Competitive Pricing:</strong> Get wholesale value on bulk apparel and everyday blank clothing.<br/></li><li><strong>Quality You Can Count On:</strong> Consistent products backed by helpful customer support.<br/></li><li><strong>No Minimums:</strong> Order a few to test styles or buy bulk when you’re ready to stock up.<br/></li><li><strong>Huge Selection:</strong> Shop sizes, colors, fits, and top brands across every category.<br/></li><li><strong>Fast Delivery:</strong> Restock quickly and keep production moving without delays.</li></ul><p></p><p>Ready to stock up? Browse best sellers above or shop by category to find the right blank apparel for your next run.</p>",
            "text_size": "regular"
          }
        }
      },
